you and DiffuseStar's manager.

292
00:15:59,239 --> 00:16:00,760
The employees can testify

293
00:16:00,760 --> 00:16:02,280
that you took part in the scriptwriting.

294
00:16:02,520 --> 00:16:03,280
So what?

295
00:16:03,640 --> 00:16:05,280
