326
00:17:55,479 --> 00:17:56,160
Wait for me.

327
00:17:56,359 --> 00:17:57,400
I have good news for you.

328
00:18:02,239 --> 00:18:03,479
Good news?

329
00:18:13,160 --> 00:18:13,880
How much is left?

330
00:18:14,040 --> 00:18:14,800
Send it to me.

331
