367
00:19:56,719 --> 00:19:57,359
No problem.

368
00:19:57,560 --> 00:19:58,640
Not only that,

369
00:19:59,839 --> 00:20:02,439
I can even offer myself to you.

370
00:20:05,589 --> 00:20:07,640
Who do you learn this from?

371
00:20:09,640 --> 00:20:10,199
